short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An offline/online JSON Editor for chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
JSONEdit is a free and open source json editor based on the Online JSON Editor made by Jos de Jong, the main difference between the original version and this is:
- JSONEdit runs as a application rather than a website.
- JSONEdit have small design changes.

JSONEdit works offline on Windows, Linux, Mac and Chrome OS/Chromium
